Dialogue: 0,0:00:02.36,0:00:05.03,Default,,0,0,0,,What can you do on a social network?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:05.03,0:00:07.99,Default,,0,0,0,,You can connect with people;
Dialogue: 0,0:00:07.99,0:00:10.24,Default,,0,0,0,,(a {\i1}{s18}{nSerif}lot{
} of people)
Dialogue: 0,0:00:11.32,0:00:13.36,Default,,0,0,0,,share your photos;
Dialogue: 0,0:00:15.29,0:00:17.33,Default,,0,0,0,,tell jokes;
Dialogue: 0,0:00:18.16,0:00:20.20,Default,,0,0,0,,post your thoughts on,
Dialogue: 0,0:00:20.21,0:00:23.26,Default,,0,0,0,,well, just about anything;
Dialogue: 0,0:00:23.25,0:00:25.67,Default,,0,0,0,,And see what all your friends are up to.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:25.67,0:00:27.76,Default,,0,0,0,,It’s pretty easy
Dialogue: 0,0:00:27.76,0:00:29.97,Default,,0,0,0,,—and th{\i1}{s18}{nSerif}at’s th{
}e problem.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:29.97,0:00:33.39,Default,,0,0,0,,Sometimes it’s a little to{\i1}{s18}{nSerif}o {
}easy.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:33.39,0:00:36.56,Default,,0,0,0,,You see, a social network may look harmless,
Dialogue: 0,0:00:36.56,0:00:38.60,Default,,0,0,0,,but once you log in,
Dialogue: 0,0:00:38.60,0:00:40.64,Default,,0,0,0,,watch out!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:40.64,0:00:42.68,Default,,0,0,0,,It could be a dangerous place.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:44.40,0:00:47.07,Default,,0,0,0,,So if your parents\Nallow you to have an account,
Dialogue: 0,0:00:47.07,0:00:49.07,Default,,0,0,0,,you have to be smart,
Dialogue: 0,0:00:49.07,0:00:51.07,Default,,0,0,0,,social-network smart.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:51.07,0:00:53.07,Default,,0,0,0,,Follow the front-page rule.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:53.07,0:00:55.07,Default,,0,0,0,,Don’t post anything
Dialogue: 0,0:00:55.08,0:00:57.92,Default,,0,0,0,,that you wouldn’t want to see on the TV news
Dialogue: 0,0:00:57.91,0:01:01.00,Default,,0,0,0,,or the front page of the newspaper.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:01.00,0:01:04.71,Default,,0,0,0,,And that includes\Npersonal information like
Dialogue: 0,0:01:04.71,0:01:06.71,Default,,0,0,0,,your phone number,
Dialogue: 0,0:01:06.71,0:01:08.38,Default,,0,0,0,,where you live,
Dialogue: 0,0:01:08.38,0:01:11.05,Default,,0,0,0,,and where you go to school.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:11.05,0:01:13.64,Default,,0,0,0,,Never tell people when you’re not home
Dialogue: 0,0:01:13.64,0:01:15.81,Default,,0,0,0,,or when you’re going on vacation.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:15.80,0:01:18.18,Default,,0,0,0,,It may seem harmless,
Dialogue: 0,0:01:18.18,0:01:21.02,Default,,0,0,0,,but that’s exactly the kind of information
Dialogue: 0,0:01:21.02,0:01:24.02,Default,,0,0,0,,thieves can use to break into your house
Dialogue: 0,0:01:24.02,0:01:26.69,Default,,0,0,0,,or even steal your identity!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:27.98,0:01:31.03,Default,,0,0,0,,Now let’s look at your reputation.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:31.03,0:01:34.95,Default,,0,0,0,,Your photos and comments say a lot about you.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:34.95,0:01:38.41,Default,,0,0,0,,So, if you’ve made a fool of yourself, ask,
Dialogue: 0,0:01:38.41,0:01:41.29,Default,,0,0,0,,‘Is this how I really want people to view me
Dialogue: 0,0:01:41.29,0:01:43.75,Default,,0,0,0,,—not just now but in the future,
Dialogue: 0,0:01:43.75,0:01:46.17,Default,,0,0,0,,like at a job interview?’
Dialogue: 0,0:01:46.17,0:01:48.30,Default,,0,0,0,,At Proverbs 22:1,
Dialogue: 0,0:01:48.30,0:01:50.97,Default,,0,0,0,,the Bible says a good reputation
Dialogue: 0,0:01:50.97,0:01:53.18,Default,,0,0,0,,is ‘worth more than silver and gold.’
Dialogue: 0,0:01:54.30,0:01:56.59,Default,,0,0,0,,Don’t let that Delete key fool you.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:56.60,0:01:59.60,Default,,0,0,0,,Posting something on any social network
Dialogue: 0,0:01:59.60,0:02:02.35,Default,,0,0,0,,is kind of like writing in permanent ink.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:04.85,0:02:08.15,Default,,0,0,0,,OK, so you’re careful \Nabout wh{\i1}{s18}{nSerif}at {
}you share.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:08.15,0:02:11.03,Default,,0,0,0,,Now think\Nabout {\i1}{s18}{nSerif}who {
} you’re sharing it with.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:11.03,0:02:13.03,Default,,0,0,0,,Who are your friends?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:13.03,0:02:15.83,Default,,0,0,0,,Some people have hundreds of online friends.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:15.82,0:02:18.11,Default,,0,0,0,,Some have thousands.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:18.12,0:02:21.21,Default,,0,0,0,,So you may think,\N‘The more friends, the better, right?’
Dialogue: 0,0:02:21.20,0:02:23.20,Default,,0,0,0,,Actually, no!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:23.21,0:02:27.17,Default,,0,0,0,,That kind of thinking\Ncan blow up in your face.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:28.54,0:02:31.79,Default,,0,0,0,,You see,\Nwhen you connect with online friends,
Dialogue: 0,0:02:31.80,0:02:35.43,Default,,0,0,0,,you are also indirectly connecting\Nwith {\i1}{s18}{nSerif}their{
} friends
Dialogue: 0,0:02:35.43,0:02:37.93,Default,,0,0,0,,And their {\i1}{s18}{nSerif}friends’ {
}friends.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:37.93,0:02:41.18,Default,,0,0,0,,That means\Nyou may find yourself seeing posts
Dialogue: 0,0:02:41.18,0:02:43.56,Default,,0,0,0,,from people you don’t even know
Dialogue: 0,0:02:43.56,0:02:46.81,Default,,0,0,0,,—people whose morals and beliefs\Nmay be different from yours.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:46.81,0:02:48.81,Default,,0,0,0,,They may use bad language
Dialogue: 0,0:02:48.81,0:02:52.27,Default,,0,0,0,,or post about things you {\i1}{s18}{nSerif}know are wrong.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:52.28,0:02:55.62,Default,,0,0,0,,Those just aren’t the kind of friends\Nyou want to hang around with
Dialogue: 0,0:02:55.61,0:02:58.20,Default,,0,0,0,,—not even online.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:58.20,0:03:00.24,Default,,0,0,0,,And there’s another danger.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:00.24,0:03:02.24,Default,,0,0,0,,At Psalm 26:4,
Dialogue: 0,0:03:02.24,0:03:05.74,Default,,0,0,0,,the Bible warns about people\N“who hide what they are.”
Dialogue: 0,0:03:05.75,0:03:08.21,Default,,0,0,0,,They pretend to be someone they are not
Dialogue: 0,0:03:08.21,0:03:12.51,Default,,0,0,0,,and may seem super friendly,
Dialogue: 0,0:03:12.50,0:03:15.30,Default,,0,0,0,,but they can be dangerous.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:17.55,0:03:21.60,Default,,0,0,0,,So when it comes to friends,\Nyou need to be picky.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:22.77,0:03:24.86,Default,,0,0,0,,The safest friends {\i1}{s18}{nSerif}online 
Dialogue: 0,0:03:24.85,0:03:27.77,Default,,0,0,0,,are ones you already know {\i1}{s18}{nSerif}offline.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:27.77,0:03:29.98,Default,,0,0,0,,There’s one more thing to think about:
Dialogue: 0,0:03:29.98,0:03:31.98,Default,,0,0,0,,It has to do with your {\i1}{s18}{nSerif}time.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:31.98,0:03:36.19,Default,,0,0,0,,Checking out the latest posts\Ncan be addictive.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:36.20,0:03:39.04,Default,,0,0,0,,So let’s set some limits,
Dialogue: 0,0:03:39.03,0:03:41.32,Default,,0,0,0,,and don’t let your on{\i1}{s18}{nSerif}line l{
}ife
Dialogue: 0,0:03:41.33,0:03:43.75,Default,,0,0,0,,get in the way of your {\i1}{s18}{nSerif}real{
} life.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:45.45,0:03:48.29,Default,,0,0,0,,You know,\Nconnecting with others online
Dialogue: 0,0:03:48.29,0:03:50.29,Default,,0,0,0,,can be fun and safe
Dialogue: 0,0:03:50.29,0:03:53.25,Default,,0,0,0,,as long as you look out for all the dangers.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:56.13,0:03:59.93,Default,,0,0,0,,So the next time you log in, be smart,
Dialogue: 0,0:03:59.93,0:04:02.47,Default,,0,0,0,,social-network smart.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:02.19,0:00:05.07,Default2,,0,0,0,,ソーシャルネットワークで\N何ができますか？\N
Dialogue: 0,0:00:05.07,0:00:07.95,Default2,,0,0,0,,みんなとつながることができます\N
Dialogue: 0,0:00:07.95,0:00:10.01,Default2,,0,0,0,,しかも大勢の人とです\N
Dialogue: 0,0:00:11.53,0:00:14.00,Default2,,0,0,0,,写真をシェアしたり—\N
Dialogue: 0,0:00:15.24,0:00:18.91,Default2,,0,0,0,,冗談を言ったり—\N
Dialogue: 0,0:00:18.91,0:00:22.00,Default2,,0,0,0,,いろんなことについて\N自分の意見を言ったり—\N
Dialogue: 0,0:00:23.13,0:00:25.84,Default2,,0,0,0,,みんなが今何しているかが分かります\N
Dialogue: 0,0:00:25.84,0:00:27.64,Default2,,0,0,0,,すっごく簡単—\N
Dialogue: 0,0:00:27.63,0:00:30.47,Default2,,0,0,0,,でも そこが問題です\N
Dialogue: 0,0:00:30.47,0:00:34.02,Default2,,0,0,0,,簡単過ぎることがあるんです\N
Dialogue: 0,0:00:34.01,0:00:37.14,Default2,,0,0,0,,害がないように思えるかもしれません\N
Dialogue: 0,0:00:37.14,0:00:40.77,Default2,,0,0,0,,でも 一度ログインしたら気を付けて！\N
Dialogue: 0,0:00:40.77,0:00:43.00,Default2,,0,0,0,,危険がいっぱいです\N
Dialogue: 0,0:00:44.86,0:00:48.49,Default2,,0,0,0,,ですから 親にアカウントの取得を\N許可してもらえたら—\N
Dialogue: 0,0:00:48.49,0:00:51.49,Default2,,0,0,0,,十分注意して利用してください\N
Dialogue: 0,0:00:51.49,0:00:54.45,Default2,,0,0,0,,基本的なルールを守りましょう\N
Dialogue: 0,0:00:54.45,0:01:00.00,Default2,,0,0,0,,テレビや新聞のニュースに載せられたら\N困るようなものを投稿してはなりません\N
Dialogue: 0,0:01:01.79,0:01:04.75,Default2,,0,0,0,,個人情報も載せてはなりません\N
Dialogue: 0,0:01:04.75,0:01:10.00,Default2,,0,0,0,,電話番号とか 住所とか 学校名などです\N
Dialogue: 0,0:01:11.55,0:01:15.10,Default2,,0,0,0,,いつ家にいないとか\Nいつ旅行に出かけるとかも—\N
Dialogue: 0,0:01:15.10,0:01:17.19,Default2,,0,0,0,,書き込んではいけません\N
Dialogue: 0,0:01:17.18,0:01:19.77,Default2,,0,0,0,,問題がないように思える\Nかもしれませんが—\N
Dialogue: 0,0:01:19.77,0:01:21.56,Default2,,0,0,0,,犯罪者にとっては—\N
Dialogue: 0,0:01:21.56,0:01:24.23,Default2,,0,0,0,, 泥棒に入ったり\Nあなたになりすましたりするのに—\N
Dialogue: 0,0:01:24.23,0:01:27.00,Default2,,0,0,0,,おいしい情報なのです！\N
Dialogue: 0,0:01:28.53,0:01:31.37,Default2,,0,0,0,,あなたの評判についてはどうですか？\N
Dialogue: 0,0:01:31.36,0:01:35.82,Default2,,0,0,0,,写真やコメントは\Nあなたについて多くを語ります\N
Dialogue: 0,0:01:35.82,0:01:37.62,Default2,,0,0,0,,恥ずかしいものを載せたら—\N
Dialogue: 0,0:01:37.62,0:01:41.29,Default2,,0,0,0,,それを見た人はあなたについて\Nどんな印象を持つでしょうか？\N
Dialogue: 0,0:01:41.29,0:01:46.80,Default2,,0,0,0,,将来 仕事の面接の結果にも\N影響するかもしれません\N
Dialogue: 0,0:01:46.79,0:01:49.79,Default2,,0,0,0,,聖書の箴言 22章1節によると—\N
Dialogue: 0,0:01:49.80,0:01:53.00,Default2,,0,0,0,,良い評判には\N銀や“金”よりも価値があります\N
Dialogue: 0,0:01:55.05,0:01:57.97,Default2,,0,0,0,,いつでも消せると思ってはなりません\N
Dialogue: 0,0:01:57.97,0:02:02.00,Default2,,0,0,0,,一度投稿したものは\Nいつまでも残るからです\N
Dialogue: 0,0:02:05.44,0:02:07.57,Default2,,0,0,0,,何をシェアするかだけでなく— \N
Dialogue: 0,0:02:07.56,0:02:11.19,Default2,,0,0,0,,だれとシェアするかにも注意が必要です\N
Dialogue: 0,0:02:11.19,0:02:13.32,Default2,,0,0,0,,どんな友達がいますか？\N
Dialogue: 0,0:02:13.32,0:02:17.95,Default2,,0,0,0,,SNSの友達が\N数百人 数千人という人もいます\N
Dialogue: 0,0:02:17.95,0:02:20.00,Default2,,0,0,0,,多ければ多いほど良い\Nということでしょうか？\N
Dialogue: 0,0:02:21.33,0:02:23.17,Default2,,0,0,0,,そうではありません\N
Dialogue: 0,0:02:23.16,0:02:26.00,Default2,,0,0,0,,思い違いをしていると\N大変なことになります\N
Dialogue: 0,0:02:29.00,0:02:31.80,Default2,,0,0,0,,オンラインで友達とつながっている時には—\N
Dialogue: 0,0:02:31.80,0:02:35.35,Default2,,0,0,0,,その人の友達とも\N間接的につながっています\N
Dialogue: 0,0:02:35.34,0:02:39.01,Default2,,0,0,0,,そして その友達の友達にもです\N
Dialogue: 0,0:02:39.01,0:02:41.56,Default2,,0,0,0,,つまり 全く知らない人—\N
Dialogue: 0,0:02:41.56,0:02:46.94,Default2,,0,0,0,,あなたとはモラルや信条が違う人たちの\N投稿も見えてしまうのです\N
Dialogue: 0,0:02:46.94,0:02:49.53,Default2,,0,0,0,,汚い言葉を使う人や— \N
Dialogue: 0,0:02:49.52,0:02:52.77,Default2,,0,0,0,,良くないものを投稿する人もいます\N
Dialogue: 0,0:02:52.78,0:02:56.45,Default2,,0,0,0,,そんな人たちと一緒にいたいとは\N思わないはずです\N
Dialogue: 0,0:02:56.45,0:02:59.62,Default2,,0,0,0,,ネット上でも同じです\N
Dialogue: 0,0:02:59.62,0:03:01.54,Default2,,0,0,0,,別の危険もあります\N
Dialogue: 0,0:03:01.54,0:03:04.75,Default2,,0,0,0,,聖書の詩編 26編4節によると—\N
Dialogue: 0,0:03:04.75,0:03:08.13,Default2,,0,0,0,,“自分がどんな者かを隠す”人がいます\N
Dialogue: 0,0:03:08.13,0:03:12.51,Default2,,0,0,0,,別人になりすまして すごく親切な\Nふりをするのです\N
Dialogue: 0,0:03:12.50,0:03:15.00,Default2,,0,0,0,,そこに落とし穴があります\N
Dialogue: 0,0:03:18.26,0:03:22.00,Default2,,0,0,0,,ですから 友達はよく選びましょう\N
Dialogue: 0,0:03:23.06,0:03:24.10,Default2,,0,0,0,,安全なのは—\N
Dialogue: 0,0:03:24.10,0:03:28.86,Default2,,0,0,0,,オフラインですでに知っている人を\N友達にすることです\N
Dialogue: 0,0:03:28.85,0:03:32.19,Default2,,0,0,0,,もうひとつ大切なのは 時間です\N
Dialogue: 0,0:03:32.19,0:03:36.49,Default2,,0,0,0,,最新の投稿をチェックしていると\Nきりがありません\N
Dialogue: 0,0:03:36.49,0:03:39.41,Default2,,0,0,0,,ですから 制限を設けましょう\N
Dialogue: 0,0:03:39.41,0:03:43.00,Default2,,0,0,0,,実生活に影響が及ばないように\Nするのです\N
Dialogue: 0,0:03:46.12,0:03:50.00,Default2,,0,0,0,,SNSで楽しく安全に\Nみんなとつながっているには—\N
Dialogue: 0,0:03:50.00,0:03:54.00,Default2,,0,0,0,,潜んでいる危険に\Nよく注意していなければなりません\N
Dialogue: 0,0:03:56.84,0:03:58.72,Default2,,0,0,0,,次回 ログインする時は—\N
Dialogue: 0,0:03:58.72,0:04:00.08,Default2,,0,0,0,, 賢く スマートに利用してくださいね\N
